Vegan Fried Rice (Nasi Goreng Vegan)

Ingredients:
1 plate cooked white rice
1/2 cup mixed vegetables (carrot, peas, corn)
2 cloves garlic (minced)
2 tbsp sweet soy sauce (kecap manis)
1 tbsp soy sauce
Salt & pepper to taste
Cooking oil

Instructions:
Heat oil, sauté garlic until fragrant.
Add vegetables, cook until slightly tender.
Add rice and mix well.
Season with sweet soy sauce, soy sauce, salt, and pepper.
Stir until heated through, then serve.
